 reviewed the essential stewart james yet you can be the first   × free shipping to united states of america shipping internationally can be expensive therefore for selected products including this one we are offering a free flatpack shipping alternative how our free economy shipping works we repackage the product to make it as thin and inexpensive to ship as possible for example dvds will be repackaged into our vanishing inc branded sleeves where possible we will include the original packaging but will not include boxes when the order arrives you can use your own dvd box or just use our dvd sleeve if all products in your cart are eligible for flatpack shipping we will ship your order for free an order cannot be mixed if you add a noneligible product to your order youll need to select a paidfor shipping option for the entire order when your order will arrive eligible orders are sent untracked and uninsured using a standard letter service this means that the order could take anywhere between two and six weeks to arrive regretably using this service we cannot gurantee delivery times tracking updates or replace lost packages like we can with our paidfor shipping options close × how our uk shipping works we ship to you directly from within the uk while most other uk magic shops hide what happens behind the scenes we want you to know exactly how things work heres the timeline sending to our uk warehouse typically takes    days we send uk orders in batch to the uk from our usa warehouse every day this way you avoid expensive international shipping fees and taxes we keep our most popular products in stock in the uk so often this step is skipped repacking and sending to you we send packages out via myhermes the same day that we receive them this is a popular secure trackable courier service we send you tracking info typically takes  days as soon as the package is dispatched youll receive a link to track it on this page while they dont offer any guarantees myhermes tend to d